      • setVariable

        public ValueAbstractState setVariable​(int index,
                                      ValueAbstractState state,
                                      ValueAbstractState defaultState)
        Sets the indexth position of the variable array to state and returns state. If the array has to be extended, the added cells are padded with defaultState.

        If the value is an IdentifiedReferenceValue, the corresponding heap value is also updated.
